    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="kicker">Demo</div>
        <h1>Supply Chain Copilot</h1>
        <p class="lead">Predict shortages, optimize sourcing, and support procurement decisions.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          Disruptions in global supply chains delay vehicle launches and increase costs. The Copilot continuously monitors supplier performance, logistics, and external signals to anticipate risks.
        </p>

        <h2>Process</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Continuous monitoring of supplier & logistics data.</li>
          <li>Shortage risk detection (e.g., semiconductor lead time spike).</li>
          <li>Scenario simulation: alternative sourcing, safety stock, adjusted production.</li>
          <li>Decision support → Procurement Agent → GEORGE.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Key Benefits</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Early warning system for bottlenecks.</li>
          <li>Decision transparency through simulations.</li>
          <li>Stronger supplier collaboration and negotiation.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
